  "content": " Problem</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-title\">\n    Vague Ideas<br>\n    <span class=\"highlight-red\">Don't Ship.</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"slide-subtitle\" style=\"font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 28px;\">\n    Starting points that aren't actionable yet.\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"card\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-amber); padding: 28px; margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent-amber); margin-bottom: 16px;\">Starting Points</div>\n    <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 24px; flex-shrink: 0;\">&#129300;</div>\n        <div>\n          <div style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;\">\"Search recall is 37.5%\"</div>\n          <div style=\"font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 4px;\">Exact identifiers and API names get lost in embedding space. But what's the fix?</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 24px; flex-shrink: 0;\">&#129300;</div>\n        <div>\n          <div style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;\">\"Knowledge should have a lifecycle\"</div>\n          <div style=\"font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 4px;\">Entries shouldn't live forever at the same priority. But how should they decay?</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 24px; flex-shrink: 0;\">&#129300;</div>\n        <div>\n          <div style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;\">\"The retriever is a monolith\"</div>\n          <div style=\"font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 4px;\">Can't swap components or benchmark alternatives without rewriting everything.</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 24px; flex-shrink: 0;\">&#129300;</div>\n        <div>\n          <div style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;\">\"Agents need session history\"</div>",
